<h2>1. The Service</h2>
<p>Launch.Skin provides boutique web development, clinical hosting, and vanity URL provisioning. By securing a license, you are commissioning a professional digital address (e.g., launch.skin/yourname) designed to establish authority in the aesthetics industry.</p>

<h2>2. The Lifetime Deal (LTD) Terms</h2>
<p>The "Lifetime Deal" refers to a one-time setup and licensing fee of $99. This covers the operational lifetime of the Launch.Skin platform. Under this agreement:</p>
<ul>
    <li>You are exempt from monthly or annual hosting fees.</li>
    <li>We provide ongoing technical maintenance of the underlying code stack.</li>
    <li>Should the platform ever cease operations, we will provide you with the static files of your clinical site for your own records.</li>
</ul>

<h2>3. Vanity URL Policy</h2>
<p>Vanity URLs are issued on a first-come, first-served basis. Launch.Skin reserves the right to reclaim or suspend a URL if it is used for "cybersquatting," infringes upon a registered trademark, or is used to impersonate another practitioner.</p>

<h2>4. Clinical Responsibility</h2>
<p>You are solely responsible for the accuracy of the clinical information, pricing, and medical claims displayed on your homepage. Launch.Skin is a technology provider and does not verify the medical licenses or credentials of its users. You agree to indemnify Launch.Skin against any claims arising from your clinical practice.</p>

<h2>5. Intellectual Property</h2>
<p>You retain full ownership of your logos, clinical photography, and brand identity. Launch.Skin retains ownership of the "launch.skin" domain architecture, the custom-developed source code, and the design templates used to build your masterpiece.</p>

<h2>6. Governing Law</h2>
<p>These terms are governed by the laws of the State of Delaware, USA. Any disputes shall be settled in the courts of Delaware jurisdiction.</p>

<hr class="my-8" />

<p>For clarifications on these terms or to discuss bulk licensing for multiple clinics, please <a href="/contact">Contact our Technical Team</a>.</p>
